{"article_id":"xoMMz1Ed9DmxAk0Q","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Ahead of the release of his House GOP budget Tuesday , Rep. Paul Ryan previewed some of the plan ' s key provisions ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"which","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"he claims","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"will lead to a balanced federal budget in a decade .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"`` On Tuesday , we 're introducing a budget","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that balances in 10 years -","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"without raising taxes .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"How do we do it ?","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"We stop spending money","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"the government does n't have , ''","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Ryan wrote in an editorial","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"published on the Wall Street Journal 's website Monday .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Savings would come from a series of measures","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that have long been backed by Republicans .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"One is a repeal of President Barack Obama 's sweeping health care law ,","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"which continues to be implemented","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"after being deemed constitutional by the U.S. Supreme Court last summer .","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"Ryan 's plan would replace the law with what he called `` patient-centered reforms . ''","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"One of those would be a major change to Medicare","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"starting in 2024 ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"when Ryan 's plan stipulates","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"seniors would have a choice of health care plans ,","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"including traditional Medicare .","depth":14},{"id":24,"text":"Seniors would receive support from the government toward paying their premiums","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"based on their income level and health .","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"In the op-ed , he writes ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"`` Those in or near retirement will see no changes ,","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"and future beneficiaries will inherit a program","depth":14},{"id":29,"text":"they can count on . ''","depth":14},{"id":30,"text":"Ryan recently backed off a proposal","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"to make changes to Medicare for people under the age of 57 -","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"GOP aides said","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"an analysis of the two-year difference showed","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"it would not save the federal government a significant amount of money .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"In his editorial , Ryan writes","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"his plan would open government-owned land to energy development ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and would include approval for the Keystone XL pipeline , a project","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that 's been delayed by the Obama administration .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Ryan also says","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"mimicking the welfare reform laws of the 1990s on other federal aid programs would save money","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"and reduce the number of Americans","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"dependent on the federal government .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"And he adds","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"that tax reform","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"that closes loopholes","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"and consolidates rates","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"would help Americans save billions of dollars per year .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"`` Our opponents will shout austerity ,","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"but let 's put this in perspective , ''","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"Ryan writes .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"`` On the current path , we 'll spend $ 46 trillion over the next 10 years .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"Under our proposal , we 'll spend $ 41 trillion .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"On the current path , spending will increase by 5 % each year .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Under our proposal , it will increase by 3.4 % .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Because the U.S. economy will grow faster than spending ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"the budget will balance by 2023 ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"and debt","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"held by the public","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"will drop to just over half the size of the economy . ''","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Ryan 's full budget , with further details of his proposed measures and cuts , will be unveiled Tuesday morning .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":121,"left":0,"right":120,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":120,"left":119,"right":60,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":107,"right":118,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":107,"left":64,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":1,"right":63,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":62,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":62,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":71,"right":105,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":66,"right":70,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":65,"right":7,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":8,"right":69,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":67,"right":68,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":67,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":72,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":91,"right":103,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":91,"left":86,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":75,"right":85,"re